  <title>Arguments</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Arguments</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Argument lists are used when calling methods or functions that expect parameters. &#160;There are 2 syntaxes. One that allows named arguments (for the Core dialect when calling functions and methods) and one that does not allow named arguments (used for Properties). The syntax for these argument lists is:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:italic; color:#000000;">// NOTE: Separate rule for bracketedarguments because they cannot use idendifierName syntax</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">bracketedArgumentList &#160; </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><tab /><tab /><tab /><tab /><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">: unnamedArgument (COMMA unnamedArgument)*</text><br/><tab /><tab /><tab /><tab /><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">;</text><br/><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">unnamedArgument &#160; &#160;: &#160;expression?</text><br/><tab /><tab /><tab /><tab /><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">argumentList</text><tab /><tab /><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">: &#160;namedArgument (COMMA namedArgument)*</text><br/><tab /><tab /><tab /><tab /><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">;</text><br/></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:italic; color:#000000;">// NOTE: Expression is optional so we can skip arguments for VO/Vulcan compatibility</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">namedArgument</text><tab /><tab /><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">: &#160;identifierName ASSIGN_OP &#160;( (REF | OUT) )? expression?</text><br/><tab /><tab /><tab /><tab /><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">| &#160;( (REF | OUT) )? expression?</text><br/><tab /><tab /><tab /><tab /><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">;</text><br/></para>
  </body>
